  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">LOOP 语句</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">用途</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">LOOP 语句会使控制跳回到最内层的 FOR、FOREACH、REPEAT 或 DO WHILE 语句的开头。</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box">LOOP</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">备注</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">LOOP 语句只能在 DO WHILE、FOR ... NEXT、FOREACH .. NEXT 或 REPEAT .. UNTIL 结构内有效。在这些结构之外使用 LOOP 语句将引发编译时错误。</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">参见<br/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="command_DO_WHILE" styleclass="Body Text">DO WHILE </link><br/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="command_FOR" styleclass="Body Text">FOR </link></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="command_FOREACH">FOREACH</link><br/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="command_REPEAT_UNTIL">REPEAT UNTIL </link></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"></para>
  </body>
